  "text": "Two-hybrid assay was performed following the manufacturer's instructions (Clonetech Matchmaker II). For cloning in the twohybrid vectors, cDNA was amplified by PCR using Phusion Taq polymerase (Finzyme). PCR products were digested and cloned in either pAS-1 or pACT-II as indicated in the figure. The fission yeast vector expressing HA-Mcs2 or HA-Pch1 was previously described [CITATION_1] .",
